<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #0d9488;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #0d9488;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px 0;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background: #f0fdfa;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        margin-top: 40px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Sustainable Software Manifesto</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Verify your email address</h2>

      <p>Thank you for starting your signature for the Sustainable Software Manifesto! To verify your email and complete your signature, please enter the following code:</p>

      <div class="code">
        <%= @verification_code %>
      </div>

      <p>This code will verify your email address: <strong><%= @signature.email %></strong></p>

      <p>If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Sustainable Software Manifesto<br>
      Building a better future through sustainable software development</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
